emepackage\"></a>\nOur Xtreme package <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">provides all of the services included in the Nhanced</span> Package and adds the following enhancements to make sure you and your guests have a memorable evening.\n<ol>\n	<li><strong>Visualization Show </strong>- A custom picture show, created from your treasured photographs that can be shown throughout the entire Event. This service enables you to share with your guests the special memories of your family that brought you to this special day, adding a personal touch that will make your party unforgettable.</li>\n	<li><strong>Music Visualization </strong>- A visualization show of laser lights projected on a screen that complements both the music and lighting.</li>\n	<li><strong>Xtreme Lighting </strong>- 2 LED lighting systems, including a Strobe on a truss system.</li>\n</ol>\n<em><strong>COST: $1049.99</strong></em>\n<strong>ADDITIONAL OPTIONS:</strong> <em>(all available at additional charges - a discount is given when you purchase multiple packages with us)</em>\n<strong><em>American Idol Contest via Karaoke</em></strong>\nKaraoke (bimoraic clipped compound of Japanese kara \"empty\" and okesutora \"orchestra\"), Japanese: [karaoke] is a form of interactive entertainment or video game in which amateur singers sing along with recorded music (a music video) using a microphone and public address system. The music is typically a well-known pop song minus the lead vocal. Lyrics are usually displayed on a video screen, along with a moving symbol, changing color, or music video images, to guide the singer. It is also a term used by recording engineers translated as \"empty track\" meaning there is no vocal track.\n<strong><em>Photo Booth</em></strong>\n<em>Having a portable Photo Booth at your event makes for an unforgetable event. Guests are allowed unlimited turns in the booth as a </em><em>keepsake disc can be made of the pictures taken.</em> <em>Photo Strips can be produced and they can be customized with your personalized graphic. Inquire about pricing.</em>\n<strong><em>Custom Voice Overs</em></strong>\nPre-recorded special messages can be edited and customized to your musical selections.\n<strong><em>Party Props/Giveaways</em></strong>\n<em>No one (young or old) ever seems to outgrow playing with toys. This is why having them at your celebration is an added bonus. Given out during the sounds of an upbeat tempo and while guests are on the dance floor, giveaways enhance the fun that much more. And who doesn\'t like to win a prize after competing in a floor game!  We offer 3 levels of props - please inquire.</em>\n<strong><em>Additional Staff</em></strong>\nDancers (for example) can be provided to interact with the guests and initiate dancing and fun!\n<strong><em>LED Reception Hall Lighting</em></strong>\n\n<strong><em>Bubble and Fog Machines</em></strong>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n'),(30,'Movie','Inquiry','\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n<p align=\"left\">If you choose our services, we will send an invoice detailing the package you have chosen.\n<p align=\"left\">Our movie screens work excellent for both indoor as well as outdoor use. Flat screen and rear projection are available.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"> Package Includes:</p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">ONE OF THE FOLLOWING SCREENS--12\'BY 12\' INFLATABLE SCREEN (actual screen size is 10\'X6\'), 10\'X 6\' FLAT SCREEN or 5\' x 4\' REAR PROJECTION SCREEN</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">PROJECTOR</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">DVD PLAYER</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">SOUND SYSTEM</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">SET UP AND BREAKDOWN</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">3 HOUR USAGE</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p align=\"center\"><em><strong>COST:       $ 229.99</strong></em></p>\n<p align=\"center\"> We set up the equipment, provide instructions, then return for the pick up. We require a $100.00 deposit to make a reservation. The balance plus a $300.00 security deposit are both required upon set up. The $300.00 security deposit will be returned when we pick up the equipment. Prices subject to change on Holidays. </p>\n\n</div>\n'),(31,'PB','Inquiry','<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"infobox\">\n<p align=\"left\">If you choose our services, we\'d send an invoice to you detailing the package you have chosen. A Photo Booth creates a lifelong memory and a lasting memento of the occasion. We have 2 types of Photo Booths (Closed and Open) each with 3 party packages available.</p>\n<p align=\"left\"> <em>FEW THINGS TO NOTE: </em></p>\n<p align=\"left\"> An Open Style Booth has no separating medium that gives the guests being photographed a level of privacy as the photo session can be seen by others. A Closed Style Booth does offer privacy as there are walls enclosing your guests being photographed. </p>\n<p align=\"left\"> For the Nhanced and Xtreme packages - Processing of the pictures by a technician takes place onsite only moments after the photos are taken. There are several configurations for printing photos along with the option to print a saying or announcement on each photo. </p>\n<p align=\"left\"> Pictures taken during your event can be made available on Facebook @ http://www.facebook.com/EntertainmentNBeyond or Google+! Want to see pictures of recent events - friend us on facebook. </p>\n<p align=\"left\">When choosing a vendor consider: </p>\n<ul>\n	<li> 1) item by item what you are getting for the quoted price, and you 		will find that our prices are very reasonable. </li>\n	<li> 2) Reputation and reliability: Please see our reviews on our 	contact us page and on wedding wire. </li>\n</ul>\n<p align=\"left\"> An <em>Open Style Booth</em> has no separating medium that would otherwise give the guests being photographed a level of privacy as the photo session can be seen by others.</p>\n<p align=\"left\">Our Photo Booth packages are:</p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>OPEN BOOTH BEYOND PARTY: </strong>\nPackage Includes:</p>\n<ul>\n	<li>Setup/breakdown and operation</li>\n	<li>Onsite technician provided</li>\n	<li>Prop Box (boas, Leis, goofy glasses, hats.....)</li>\n	<li>3 hour use</li>\n	<li>Pictures taken during your event can be made available on Facebook @<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/EntertainmentandBeyond\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/EntertainmentandBeyond</a> or Google+</li>\n</ul>\n<p align=\"left\"><em><strong>COST:       $399.99</strong></em></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>OPEN BOOTH NHANCED PARTY (2\" x 6\" or 4\" x 6\" option): </strong>\nPackage includes all items listed under the <em>Beyond Party </em>plus:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>2\" x 6\" Photo Print option\n<ul>\n	<li>3 poses per seating</li>\n	<li>2 copies of photo per seating</li>\n	<li>Custom title of your event on each copy</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>4\" x 6\" Photo Print option\n<ul>\n	<li>4 poses per seating</li>\n	<li>One copy of photo per seating</li>\n	<li>Custom title of your event on each copy</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<em><strong>COST:       $549.99 </strong></em>\n\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>OPEN BOOTH XTREME PARTY (2\" x 6\" Option): </strong>\nPackage includes all items listed under the <em>Beyond Party </em>plus:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>3 poses per seating</li>\n	<li>Multiple Copies (up to 8 copies per seating)</li>\n	<li>Custom title of your event on each copy</li>\n</ul>\n<em><strong>COST:       $649.99 </strong></em>\n\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>OPEN BOOTH XTREME PARTY (4\" x 6\" Option): </strong>\nPackage includes all items listed under the <em>Beyond Party </em>plus:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>4 poses per seating</li>\n	<li>Multiple Copies (up to 8 copies per seating)</li>\n	<li>Custom title of your event on each copy</li>\n</ul>\n<em><strong>COST:       $699.99 </strong></em>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>CLOSED BOOTH BEYOND PARTY:</strong>\nPackage Includes:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Setup/breakdown and operation</li>\n	<li>Onsite technician provided</li>\n	<li>Prop