- a discount is given when you purchase multiple packages with us)</em>\n<strong><em>American Idol Contest via Karaoke</em></strong>\nKaraoke (bimoraic clipped compound of Japanese kara \"empty\" and okesutora \"orchestra\"), Japanese: [karaoke] is a form of interactive entertainment or video game in which amateur singers sing along with recorded music (a music video) using a microphone and public address system. The music is typically a well-known pop song minus the lead vocal. Lyrics are usually displayed on a video screen, along with a moving symbol, changing color, or music video images, to guide the singer. It is also a term used by recording engineers translated as \"empty track\" meaning there is no vocal track.\n<strong><em>Photo Booth</em></strong>\n<em>Having a portable Photo Booth at your event makes for an unforgetable event. Guests are allowed unlimited turns in the booth as a </em><em>keepsake disc can be made of the pictures taken.</em><em> </em><em>Photo Strips can be produced and they can be customized with your personalized graphic. Inquire about pricing.</em>\n<strong><em>Custom Voice Overs</em></strong>\nPre-recorded special messages can be edited and customized to your musical selections.\n\n<strong><em>Additional Staff</em></strong>\nDancers (for example) can be provided to interact with the guests and initiate dancing and fun!\n<strong><em>Bubble and Fog Machines</em></strong>\n<br><br>\n</div>\n</div>\n'),(34,'Wedding-FU ','Inquiry','<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"infobox\">\n<p align=\"left\"><em> >Just following up to see if you have any questions regarding the services we can provide for your Wedding celebration. As previously mentioned we have several packages available. I have listed them below again for your convenience. </em></p>\n<div align=\"left\"><em>Each package features an increased level of involvement with our DJs and Entertainment Party Hosts.</em></div>\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>The wedding packages available are: