/div>\n'),(38,'Thank You','Contract','<p align=\"left\">Thank you for having us provide services to your party. It indeed was our pleasure. Please keep us in mind for future events. As a repeat customer, we\'d offer you $25 off any rental or $50.00 off of any staffed event. Thanks Again! Fred </p>\n<br><br>\n</div>\n</div>\n'),(39,'Rental Contract','Contract','\n<div class=\"infobox\">\n<p align=\"left\"><em> >A $100 Deposit is requested to hold your date. The final payment and security deposit are requested one week in advance and can be paid by credit card, Paypal, Google Checkout or check. Cash is the only form of payment accepted the day of the event. If you have any questions feel free to call us @ 215-267-702-5266 or email us at info@entertainmentandbeyond.com - Fred '),(40,'Estimate','Contract','\n<div class=\"infobox\">\n<p align=\"left\"><em> >A $200 Deposit is requested to hold your date. The final payment is requested one week in advance and can be paid by credit card, Paypal, Google Checkout or check. Cash is the only form of payment accepted the day of the event. If you have any questions feel free to call us @ 215-267-702-5266 or email us at info@entertainmentandbeyond.com - Fred '),(41,'Deposit Received','Contract','\n<div class=\"infobox\">\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Thanks for sending in your deposit. The final payment is requested one week in advance and can be paid by credit card, Paypal, Google Checkout or check. Cash is the only form of payment accepted the day of the event. If you have any questions feel free to call us @ 215-267-702-5266 or email us at info@entertainmentandbeyond.com - Fred '),(42,'Final Payment','Contract','\n<div class=\"infobox\">\n<p align=\"left\"><em> >Thanks for sending in your final payment. We are looking forward to working with you to make your event a success. If you have any questions feel free to call us @ 215-267-702-5266 or email us at info@entertainmentandbeyond.com - Fred ');
